## Update Khairina Widget

Edit `khairina-widget.js` in your landing page repo:

Find this line (near bottom):
```javascript
const WEBHOOK_URL = 'https://YOUR-N8N-INSTANCE.n8n.cloud/webhook/khairina-chat';
```

Replace with your Vercel URL:
```javascript
const WEBHOOK_URL = 'https://YOUR-VERCEL-PROJECT.vercel.app/api/khairina';
```

Example:
```javascript
const WEBHOOK_URL = 'https://ky-ryth-backend.vercel.app/api/khairina';
```

Then uncomment:
```javascript
new KhairinaChatWidget(WEBHOOK_URL);
```

