## Test Your Backend

### Using cURL:

```bash
curl -X POST https://YOUR-VERCEL-URL/api/khairina \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "message": "Hello Khairina",
    "systemPrompt": "You are Khairina, an ethical AI tutor."
  }'
```

### Expected Response:

```json
{
  "response": "Assalamualaikum! I'm Khairina. How can I help you learn today?",
  "emotionalState": "neutral",
  "isCrisis": false,
  "validated": true,
  "status": "PASS",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-05T05:45:00.000Z"
}
```

