## Update to Custom Domain

If you want `api.ky-ryth.my`:

1. Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Domains
2. Add `api.ky-ryth.my`
3. Update DNS at your domain registrar
4. Point to Vercel nameservers

Then update widget:
```javascript
const WEBHOOK_URL = 'https://api.ky-ryth.my/khairina';
```

